Packages 
Package Description
controlPanel
This package contains the functionality for the Control Panel, it supports the configuration of users, billboards and schedules.
helpers
This package includes helper methods that are used in multiple packages.
server
This package contains the functionality for the server which is a command line program and updates the database directly according to the received messages from the Control Panel back-end.
viewer
This application runs the Viewer for displaying billboards that have been scheduled from the Control Panel by connecting to the Server.
